  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Explain the polarization of a dielectric in a uniform electrical field</item>
<item>Describe the effect of a polarized dielectric on the electrical field between capacitor plates</item>
<item>Explain dielectric breakdown</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
